{
  "uuid": "468eaa109b23098ea6a8597a8b8c8beb",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Homes Content Creator",
  "description": "<h1>Homes Content Creator</h1><p><strong>Homes Content Creator (Video)</strong><br />(Real Estate & Lifestyle Content)</p><h2>About the Role</h2><p>We are looking for a <strong>Homes Content Creator</strong> to produce engaging video content focused on <strong>homes, interiors, lifestyle, and property stories</strong>.</p><p>Your role is to bring homes to life through video by capturing <strong>space, emotion, and narrative</strong>. This is not just filming houses. It’s about storytelling, trust-building, and inspiration.</p><h2>Key Responsibilities</h2><h3>Content Creation & Storytelling</h3><ul><li><p>Create short-form and long-form video content featuring homes and properties</p></li><li><p>Tell compelling stories around spaces, design choices, and lifestyle</p></li><li><p>Highlight unique selling points of each home naturally and credibly</p></li><li><p>Work with homeowners, agents, or brands during shoots</p></li></ul><h3>Filming & Production</h3><ul><li><p>Film walkthroughs, room features, and lifestyle angles</p></li><li><p>Ensure good lighting, framing, and clean audio</p></li><li><p>Capture b-roll that enhances mood and flow</p></li><li><p>Direct simple on-camera moments when needed</p></li></ul><h3>Editing & Post-Production</h3><ul><li><p>Amend storytelling and improving retention rate, to enhance video quality delivered from the editor's team.</p></li><li><p>Maintain brand aesthetics and tone</p></li></ul><h3>Platform & Performance Awareness</h3><ul><li><p>Understand what performs well in home & lifestyle content</p></li><li><p>Optimise hooks, structure, and pacing for engagement</p></li><li><p>Improve content based on feedback and performance data</p></li></ul><h2>Requirements</h2><h3>Skills & Experience</h3><ul><li><p>Experience in video content creation (portfolio required)</p></li><li><p>Strong visual sense for space, composition, and flow</p></li><li><p>Comfortable using editing tools (CapCut)</p></li><li><p>Able to communicate clearly and professionally on shoots</p></li><li><p>Basic understanding of real estate or home lifestyle content</p></li></ul><h3>Mindset & Traits</h3><ul><li><p>Detail-oriented with strong aesthetic judgment</p></li><li><p>Respectful and professional around clients’ homes</p></li><li><p>Reliable, punctual, and well-prepared</p></li><li><p>Creative and structured</p></li><li><p>Open to feedback and improvement</p></li></ul><h2>Bonus If You Have</h2><ul><li><p>Experience in real estate, interior design, or lifestyle content</p></li><li><p>Understanding of social media trends in property content</p></li><li><p>Drone filming or advanced camera skills</p></li></ul><h2>Performance Expectations</h2><ul><li><p>Consistent content output</p></li><li><p>Strong visual quality and storytelling</p></li><li><p>Ability to improve watch time and engagement</p></li><li><p>Professional conduct with clients and partners</p></li></ul><h2>Why Join Us</h2><ul><li><p>Work with beautiful homes and premium spaces</p></li><li><p>Create aspirational content that builds trust and influence</p></li><li><p>High creative ownership</p></li><li><p>Clear growth and progression opportunities</p></li></ul><h2>Growth Path</h2><ul><li><p>Senior Homes Content Creator</p></li><li><p>Content Lead (Homes)</p></li><li><p>Creative Director (Lifestyle & Homes)</p></li></ul>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 1,
